---
title: Smart Blackened Cajun Barramundi with Louisiana Sunburst Salad
description: Head down south with this dish! Flaky barramundi gets smothered in our smoky Cajun Spice and broiled until deliciously charred. A spicy sweet salad alongside packed with cranberries, almonds and greens will drive your taste buds all the way to Louisiana!

